{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-nehalist-gatsby-theme-nehalem-src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/2021-08-15-Bellman-Ford","result":{"data":{"post":{"id":"d70abeaf-2c35-5b63-873b-5a51351908c7","headings":[{"depth":2},{"depth":3},{"depth":3},{"depth":3},{"depth":2}],"frontmatter":{"title":"벨만 포드(Bellman Ford) 알고리즘","path":"/2021-08-15-Bellman-Ford","tags":["algorithm","graph"],"excerpt":"음수 cost 경로가 존재하는 그래프에서의 경로 탐색","created":"2021-08-15T00:00:00.000Z","createdPretty":"15 August, 2021","updated":"2021-08-15T00:00:00.000Z","updatedPretty":"15 August, 2021","featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"sizes":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.6666666666666667,"src":"/static/787c48f68dfa7a207f4c1da298763f81/49b19/negative_edge.png","srcSet":"/static/787c48f68dfa7a207f4c1da298763f81/dc47e/negative_edge.png 200w,\n/static/787c48f68dfa7a207f4c1da298763f81/9f2d5/negative_edge.png 400w,\n/static/787c48f68dfa7a207f4c1da298763f81/49b19/negative_edge.png 500w","sizes":"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"}}}},"html":"<h2 id=\"-벨만-포드bellman-ford-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EB%B2%A8%EB%A7%8C-%ED%8F%AC%EB%93%9Cbellman-ford-\" aria-label=\" 벨만 포드bellman ford  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>[ 벨만 포드(Bellman Ford) ]</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"negative_edge.png\"\n        title=\"negative_edge.png\"\n        src=\"/static/787c48f68dfa7a207f4c1da298763f81/0b533/negative_edge.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/787c48f68dfa7a207f4c1da298763f81/5a46d/negative_edge.png 300w,\n/static/787c48f68dfa7a207f4c1da298763f81/0b533/negative_edge.png 500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span><br>\n벨만 포드(Bellman Ford) 알고리즘은 그래프의 한 노드에서 다른 모든 노드까지의 최단 경로를 구할 수 있는 알고리즘이다. 최단 경로 알고리즘 중 하나인 다익스트라 알고리즘(<a href=\"https://goo-gy.github.io/2019-10-11-dijkstra\">https://goo-gy.github.io/2019-10-11-dijkstra</a>)보다 높은 시간 복잡도를 가진다. 대신 다익스트라 알고리즘은 그래프에 음수 cost가 있는 경우에는 사용할 수 없는 반면, Bellman Ford 알고리즘은 음수 cost가 있는 경우에도 사용할 수 있다.  </p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>음수 cost 그래프에서 적용 가능</strong>  </li>\n<li><strong>Negative Cycle 감지 가능</strong>  </li>\n<li><strong>시간 복잡도 = O(NE)</strong><br>\nN(Node의 수), E(Edge의 수)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"알고리즘\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%95%8C%EA%B3%A0%EB%A6%AC%EC%A6%98\" aria-label=\"알고리즘 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>알고리즘</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>출발 노드 설정 &#x26; 최단 거리 테이블 초기화</strong><br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/de17a2aec3f1e95a7c4ee80e1108d3d9/8c557/distance.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 28.666666666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"distance.png\"\n        title=\"distance.png\"\n        src=\"/static/de17a2aec3f1e95a7c4ee80e1108d3d9/8c557/distance.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/de17a2aec3f1e95a7c4ee80e1108d3d9/5a46d/distance.png 300w,\n/static/de17a2aec3f1e95a7c4ee80e1108d3d9/0a47e/distance.png 600w,\n/static/de17a2aec3f1e95a7c4ee80e1108d3d9/8c557/distance.png 700w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n최단 거리 테이블의 기본값은 무한(INF), 출발 노드는 0으로 초기화   </li>\n<li><strong>모든 Edge를 순회하면서 distance[src] + cost &#x3C; distance[dst] 라면 업데이트</strong>  </li>\n<li><strong>2번을 N - 1 번 반복</strong>  </li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"증명\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A6%9D%EB%AA%85\" aria-label=\"증명 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>증명</h3>\n<p>다른 부분을 제외하고 출발지에서 임의의 노드로의 최단 경로만 살펴보자.<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4c17ddd739c8375670e892aec8ea426b/6af66/shortest_path.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 15.666666666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"shortest_path.png\"\n        title=\"shortest_path.png\"\n        src=\"/static/4c17ddd739c8375670e892aec8ea426b/6af66/shortest_path.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4c17ddd739c8375670e892aec8ea426b/5a46d/shortest_path.png 300w,\n/static/4c17ddd739c8375670e892aec8ea426b/0a47e/shortest_path.png 600w,\n/static/4c17ddd739c8375670e892aec8ea426b/6af66/shortest_path.png 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span><br>\n최단 경로 순서대로 Edge를 순회한다면, 위 <code class=\"language-text\">2번 과정</code>을 한 번만 수행해도 최단 거리가 갱신된다.<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/27b9734070a668d4bca138c63782b271/6af66/update_first.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 15.666666666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"update_first.png\"\n        title=\"update_first.png\"\n        src=\"/static/27b9734070a668d4bca138c63782b271/6af66/update_first.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/27b9734070a668d4bca138c63782b271/5a46d/update_first.png 300w,\n/static/27b9734070a668d4bca138c63782b271/0a47e/update_first.png 600w,\n/static/27b9734070a668d4bca138c63782b271/6af66/update_first.png 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span><br>\n최악의 경우에도 <code class=\"language-text\">2번 과정</code>을 한 번 수행하면 최단 경로에 포함된 두 번째 노드의 최단 거리는 갱신된다.<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/42ebe3959cc1a92eda91c4cdf7119842/6af66/update_last.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 15.666666666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"update_last.png\"\n        title=\"update_last.png\"\n        src=\"/static/42ebe3959cc1a92eda91c4cdf7119842/6af66/update_last.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/42ebe3959cc1a92eda91c4cdf7119842/5a46d/update_last.png 300w,\n/static/42ebe3959cc1a92eda91c4cdf7119842/0a47e/update_last.png 600w,\n/static/42ebe3959cc1a92eda91c4cdf7119842/6af66/update_last.png 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span><br>\n마찬가지로 <code class=\"language-text\">2번 과정</code>을 한 번 수행할 때마다, 최단 경로에 있는 노드가 차례로 하나씩 최단 거리를 보장하게 된다. 그래프의 노드 수가 N이라면 <code class=\"language-text\">2번 과정</code>을 N - 1번만 수행하면 그래프 내 모든 노드까지의 최단 경로를 갱신할 수 있다.  </p>\n<h3 id=\"negative-cycle\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#negative-cycle\" aria-label=\"negative cycle permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Negative Cycle</h3>\n<p>위 증명은 그래프 내에 cost의 합이 음수가 되는 <strong>Negative Cycle</strong>이 없다고 가정했을 경우에 성립한다.<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bfb959ffec52659ec39d861b08e23455/6af66/negative_cycle.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"negative_cycle.png\"\n        title=\"negative_cycle.png\"\n        src=\"/static/bfb959ffec52659ec39d861b08e23455/6af66/negative_cycle.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bfb959ffec52659ec39d861b08e23455/5a46d/negative_cycle.png 300w,\n/static/bfb959ffec52659ec39d861b08e23455/0a47e/negative_cycle.png 600w,\n/static/bfb959ffec52659ec39d861b08e23455/6af66/negative_cycle.png 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span><br>\n그림처럼 경로 상에 <strong>Negatvie Cycle</strong>이 있다면, 최단 경로를 구하기 위해 <strong>Negative Cycle</strong>을 무한히 순회해야 하기 때문에 최단 경로를 정의하기 어렵다. 굳이 최단 거리를 따지자면 -∞이 될 것이다.  </p>\n<ul>\n<li>그래프에 Negative Cycle이 존재하는지는 어떻게 알 수 있을까.<br>\n위에서 Negative Cycle이 없을 경우 Edge를 N - 1번 순회하며 출발지에서 모든 노드까지의 최단 거리를 갱신할 수 있었다. 최단 거리가 갱신된 노드는 Distance가 업데이트될 일이 없다. 따라서 <strong>그 이후 <code class=\"language-text\">2번 과정</code>을 더 수행하였을 때, 어떤 노드든 Distance가 업데이트된다면 그래프 내에 Netgative Cycle이 있음</strong>을 알 수 있다.  </li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"-코드-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C-\" aria-label=\" 코드  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>[ 코드 ]</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cpp\"><pre class=\"language-cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token keyword\">bool</span> <span class=\"token function\">bellman_ford</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    distance_map<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> n <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> n <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span> N<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> n<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>map<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>pair<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">long</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">long</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">::</span>iterator e <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> loads<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">begin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> e <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> loads<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">end</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> e<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> src <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> e<span class=\"token operator\">-></span>first<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>first<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> dst <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> e<span class=\"token operator\">-></span>first<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>second<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">long</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">long</span> weight <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> e<span class=\"token operator\">-></span>second<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>distance_map<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>src<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> INF <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> distance_map<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>dst<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span> distance_map<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>src<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> weight<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                distance_map<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>dst<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> distance_map<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>src<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> weight<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n                <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>n <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> N<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n                    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span